N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 145.5 - Procedure in the Integrated Youth Court

State Regulations

Each case transferred from another court
to the County Court and referred to the Integrated Youth Court part thereof
shall be subject to the same substantive and procedural law as would have
applied to it had it not been transferred. Notes
